              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="testimonial-text">"My daughter's confidence in Mathematics has improved a lot. Regular tests and guidance helped her score better in board exams."</p>
          </article>

          <article class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="testimonial-top">
              <div class="testimonial-avatar">
                <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/ef/97/25/ef972507d073f998e8091814528e86d1.jpg" alt="Student testimonial" />
              </div>
