            <span class="logo-title">Maths Tuition</span>
            <span class="logo-subtitle">by Vimmy Ma'am</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="footer-tagline">
          Expert CBSE Maths coaching for Classes 10, 11 & 12 with personal attention and proven results.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4 class="footer-heading">Quick Links</h4>
